Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.81,0:23:04.23,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}恨 恨这不公的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.32,0:23:12.66,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}这座迷宫 想逃 却没有出口
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.83,0:23:16.62,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}追求自由的我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.92,0:23:25.76,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}倒立着 俯看天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.55,0:23:33.89,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我已经不是昨天的我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.14,0:23:40.90,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Shiny Shiny 夜空洒遍了星辉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.94,0:23:49.20,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}世界竟如此美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.40,0:23:56.20,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Shiny Shiny 月光载满了希望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.29,0:24:04.13,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}世界是这般精彩
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.17,0:24:06.84,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不是吗?
